{"tid":835794,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"脫毒係咪一定要玩ig","createTime":"2018-09-25T07:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T06:56:58.000Z","uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8096a994a2789d15435ed563cefc62910b32edab","tid":835794,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"平時ig只係睇人 唔會post自己相<br />\nD女仔係咪會覺得呢個男仔好毒好無自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我真係<br />\n其實我以前都好地地 <br />\n中學拍拖過一次 大學y1拍過一次 <br />\n讀左4年engine 同女人越離越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經成5年無同女仔拍過拖<br />\n唔知幾時開始連識個女仔都難<br />\n莫講話 要深入拍一場拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼見身邊好多有拖拍既男仔都會用心經營自己既ig<br />\n就算單身都好 至少都幫佢提升唔少形象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但平時我自己都唔玩ig 突然玩<br />\n覺得好突兀 沖破唔到個心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21aed2840ac63bde65070d8b67e13b9e18387fbb","tid":835794,"uid":141782,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"你係咁post 相但冇人like 會唔會仲柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0ab0c472492e678df120afba25a51d8bb7c45a","tid":835794,"uid":91192,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"脫毒係要脫毒 唔係玩ig<br />\n唔會玩玩下ig突然間唔毒"},{"pid":"7ea28aabfe5e67e75d42640f942966a0a37802e3","tid":835794,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"個look唔掂就執執佢<br />\n正常樣唔會溝唔到女"},{"pid":"ac4093663c0f15047e8f8b147fc2393b97698135","tid":835794,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"21aed2840ac63bde65070d8b67e13b9e18387fbb","tid":835794,"uid":141782,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"你係咁post 相但冇人like 會唔會仲柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:43:17.000